# .capabilitiesignore
# Glob patterns (one per line) for .cloomc files that should be skipped by
# check-capabilities-blocks.js when running in --glob mode.
# Blank lines and lines beginning with # are ignored.
# Patterns are matched against the path relative to the repo root,
# using forward slashes on all platforms.
# Supports * (any segment chars) and ** (any path depth).

# Third-party or vendored sources that are not maintained by this project
# node_modules/**
